movie.title: Mary Queen of Scots
movie.plot: Mary Stuart's (Saoirse Ronan's) attempt to overthrow her cousin Elizabeth I (Margot Robbie), Queen of England, finds her condemned to years of imprisonment before facing execution.
movie.awards: Nominated for 2 Oscars. Another 6 wins & 27 nominations.

events.title: the bridges at Samdong-ni (the inspriration for the film) are blown up in an aerial raid

movie.title: The Bridges at Toko-Ri
movie.plot: Set during the Korean War, a Navy fighter pilot must come to terms with with his own ambivalence towards the war and the fear of having to bomb a set of highly defended bridges. The ending of this grim war drama is all tension.

movie.title: Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood
movie.plot: A faded television actor and his stunt double strive to achieve fame and success in the film industry during the final years of Hollywood's Golden Age in 1969 Los Angeles.
